body:
@Kevinpsk 

While the install guide page says that `TensorFlow` requires `cudNN 5.1`,  [release notes for 1.3](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.3/RELEASE.md) says that all pre-built binaries were built with `cudNN 6`. I suspect the install guide page has not been updated.

@helxsz 
My suggestion would be to upgrade `cudNN 5.1` to `cudNN 6`
